## As a Rate
OutputE=1/TimeE
In [293]:
Egg_Model=pm.Model()
with Egg_Model:
    ### Tight parameter around the min and max temp
    TmE=pm.Normal("TmE",mu=38.889,sigma=3.0)
    Tmb=pm.Normal("Tmb",mu=10,sigma=3.0)
    ### Other parameters loose
    Rate= pm.Gamma("Rate",mu=.18,sigma=.05)
    k=pm.Normal("k",mu=1044.0,sigma=100)
    dm=pm.Gamma("dm",mu=10.00,sigma=2.00)
    dN=pm.Deterministic("dN",Rate*((((TempE-Tmb)**2)/(((TempE-Tmb)**2)+k))-tt.exp(-(TmE-(TempE-Tmb))/dm)))
    #tt.printing.Print('dn')(dN)
    obs = pm.Normal('obs', mu=dN, sigma=.0007, observed=OutputE)
    step=pm.Metropolis(vars=[TmE,Tmb,Rate,k,dm])
 
    trace=pm.sample(50000,step,cores=1)

def Simrate(Temp,TmE,TmB,k,Rate,dm):
    return(Rate*((((Temp-TmB)**2)/(((Temp-TmB)**2)+k))-np.exp(-(TmE-(Temp-TmB))/dm)))

In [26]:
### Max temp between 95 and 100
### 36.4 +-1.2


L_Model=pm.Model()
with L_Model:
    ### Tight parameter around the min and max temp
    TmL=pm.Normal("TmE",mu=36.4,sigma=1.2)
    TbL=pm.Normal("Tmb",mu=10,sigma=1.2)
    ### Other parameters loses
    RateL= pm.Gamma("Rate",mu=.016,sigma=.05)
    kL=pm.Normal("k",mu=800.0,sigma=100)
    dmL=pm.Gamma("dm",mu=6.00,sigma=6.00)
    dNL=pm.Deterministic("dN",RateL*((((TempL-TbL)**2)/(((TempL-TbL)**2)+kL))-tt.exp(-(TmL-(TempL-TbL))/dmL)))
    #tt.printing.Print('dn')(dN)
    obs = pm.Normal('obs', mu=dNL, sigma=.004, observed=OutputL)
    step=pm.Metropolis(vars=[TmL,TbL,RateL,kL,dmL])
 
    traceL=pm.sample(30000,step,cores=1)

PP_Model=pm.Model()
with PP_Model:
    ### Tight parameter around the min and max temp
    TmPP=pm.Normal("TmE",mu=37.8,sigma=.1)
    TbPP=pm.Normal("Tmb",mu=4.30,sigma=.1)
    ### Other parameters loses
    RatePP= pm.Gamma("Rate",mu=.2313,sigma=.02)
    kPP=pm.Gamma("k",mu=431.0,sigma=.1)
    dmPP=pm.Gamma("dm",mu=11.30,sigma=.01)
    dN=pm.Deterministic("dN",RatePP*((((TempPP-TbPP)**2)/(((TempPP-TbPP)**2)+kPP))-tt.exp(-(TmPP-(TempPP-TbPP))/dmPP)))
      
    #tt.printing.Print('dn')(dN)
    obs = pm.Normal('obs', mu=dN, sigma=.012, observed=OutputPP)
    step=pm.Metropolis(vars=[TmPP,TbPP,RatePP,kPP,dmPP])
 
    tracePP=pm.sample(30000,step,cores=1)

P_Model=pm.Model()
with P_Model:
    ### Tight parameter around the min and max temp
    TmP=pm.Normal("TmE",mu=30.889,sigma=2.0)
    TbP=pm.Normal("Tmb",mu=10.0,sigma=2.0)
    ### Other parameters loses
    RateP= pm.Gamma("Rate",mu=.05,sigma=.001)
    kP=pm.Gamma("k",mu=204,sigma=5)
    dmP=pm.Gamma("dm",mu=12,sigma=.1)
    dN=pm.Deterministic("dN",RateP*((((TempP-TbP)**2)/(((TempP-TbP)**2)+kP))-tt.exp(-(TmP-(TempP-TbP))/dmP)))
    #tt.printing.Print('dn')(dN)
    obs = pm.Normal('obs', mu=dN, sigma=.0005, observed=OutputP)
    step=pm.Metropolis(vars=[TmP,TbP,RateP,kP,dmP])
 
    #traceP=pm.sample(20000,tune=40000, target_accept=.85,cores=1)
    traceP=pm.sample(30000,step,cores=1)
